column16: Charlie Blackmon flies out to left fielder Jonny Gomes.
Chris Rusin singles on a sharp ground ball to first baseman Kelly Johnson.
Drew Stubbs homers (5) on a fly ball to left center field.   Brandon Barnes scores.
Wilin Rosario grounds out, shortstop Andrelton Simmons to first baseman Kelly Johnson.
Brandon Barnes doubles (10) on a line drive to center fielder Eury Perez.
Troy Tulowitzki homers (10) on a fly ball to left center field.   Charlie Blackmon scores.    DJ LeMahieu scores.
Wilin Rosario pops out to third baseman Chris Johnson in foul territory.
Brandon Barnes flies out to center fielder Cameron Maybin.
Brandon Barnes lines out softly to right fielder Nick Markakis.
Drew Stubbs called out on strikes.
Nick Hundley singles on a sharp ground ball to shortstop Andrelton Simmons, deflected by third baseman Juan Uribe.   DJ LeMahieu to 2nd.
DJ LeMahieu singles on a line drive to right fielder Nick Markakis.
Carlos Gonzalez grounds out, first baseman Chris Johnson to pitcher David Carpenter.
